skill foundation</strong></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- Horizontal separator line -->\n        <div class=\"horizontal-line\"></div>\n\n        <!-- Details Box (Bottom Section) - Text box with padding -->\n        <div class=\"details-box\">\n            <div class=\"details-title\">Charting Your Growth Trajectory</div>\n            <div class=\"details-text\">This pyramid illustrates the path for developing your skills at our company. Starting with mastering core competencies, you'll progress to expert proficiency, then managing projects effectively, and ultimately driving vision. This framework builds upon our organizational structure and promotion policies, offering a transparent view of career progression. It emphasizes continuous learning and provides a clear roadmap for achieving your professional goals and contributing to our collective success. We are invested in your growth.</div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
